comments.body:
@Namit Jain;
I've just released from HIVE-3381. Let's start looking into this.

I think this patch tries to solve two issues simultaneously. One is for merging two config to single one as mentioned above, and the other is for extending SMBOptimizer by additional conversion rule (JOIN to SMBJOIN directly), which is great. Is it possible to use it with hive.auto.convert.join=true?
